    "minides": "Citroen's mid-size SUV refreshed as the Aircross X — the only model in its segment offering a genuine 7-seat configuration, built on Citroen's signature Advanced Comfort Suspension.",
    "description": "The Citroen Aircross X (formerly C3 Aircross/Aircross) is a mid-size SUV manufactured in India, distinctive for being the only vehicle in its segment offered with both 5-seat and 7-seat layouts. It uses a 1.2-litre three-cylinder PureTech petrol engine in two states of tune — a naturally aspirated 82hp version with a 5-speed manual, and a turbocharged 110hp version with either a 6-speed manual or 6-speed torque-converter automatic. The Aircross X rides on Citroen's tuned Advanced Comfort Suspension for a smoother ride over rough roads, and the top trims add CARA, an AI-enabled multilingual voice assistant, a 10.25-inch touchscreen, ventilated front leatherette seats, ambient lighting, and a 360-degree camera with satellite view. It carries a 5-star Bharat NCAP safety rating."
  },
